- **Sameness check hit:** shares the full house skeleton with the two most recent drafts (Goldblum, Efron) — cold-open furniture, inner-thought beat, empathy-turn shape, and the templated corpus-stat sentence. Not near-verbatim enough on 3+ moves to trigger the Originality-7 cap, but real enough to dock Originality to 8 and flag for the revision pass. Side note: the **corpus count disagrees between drafts** (Tobey says 138 profiled, Goldblum says 373) — a data inconsistency worth fixing corpus-wide.

